      <section eId="sec_1381">
        <num>1381</num>
        <heading>State aid</heading>
        <subsection eId="sec_1381__subsec_a">
          <num>(a)</num>
          <content>
            <p>the first payment, not to exceed fifty per cent of the total\ngrant, shall be payable when acceptable detailed plans are approved by\nthe commissioner, and\n</p>
          </content>
        </subsection>
        <subsection eId="sec_1381__subsec_b">
          <num>(b)</num>
          <content>
            <p>the balance of the grant shall be payable when construction\ncontracts are awarded, or when construction begins, whichever occurs\nfirst.\n</p>
          </content>
        </subsection>
      </section>
